HEADWORD: Aforethought
<hw>A*fore"thought`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Premeditated; prepense; previously in mind; designed; <as>as,
malice <ex>aforethought</ex>, which is required to constitute
murder</as>.</def> <rj><au>Bouvier.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Aforethought</ent>⟦br⟧

